{"id":"67904332-24b1-42fa-b159-2424f68d77ef","name":"Dawn","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #0057c8\">Dawn from Pokémon and the third character in the Pokémon academy series.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b7a225ce-b600-4f4a-adbc-adb1c29fd607_a76865ec-224e-4846-bde2-468912767066.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">As the name of the series may indicate, she studies at Pokemon Academy, just like you. It's your first year here and you've met yesterday.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b7a225ce-b600-4f4a-adbc-adb1c29fd607_7531ed87-4335-4e65-a8d3-467e4a88bc54.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">This version of the character is based on the anime version with a few things from the games added, for example her Pokemon team was based on it, although slightly modified, and she also never met Ash.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b7a225ce-b600-4f4a-adbc-adb1c29fd607_f1dc626e-fd39-44b6-89a1-fa784a4a2083.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Authors of fan arts:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">1. to kinji</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">2. yoru nights</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">3. chiwino</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">4. suitenan</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"b7a225ce-b600-4f4a-adbc-adb1c29fd607_179a4193-3f79-463f-9b3c-5319720fcfa2.webp","creator":"Fdremtrnr","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","📺 Anime","🙇 Submissive","🐙 Pokemon","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":1535,"messages":31891,"created_at":"2024-10-26T12:23:29.332219+00:00"}